mysql> select e.emp_no, e.last_name, e.first_name, s.salary
    -> from employees e join
    ->      salaries s
    ->      on e.emp_no = s.emp_no
    -> order by s.salary asc
    -> limit 1;
+--------+-----------+------------+--------+
| emp_no | last_name | first_name | salary |
+--------+-----------+------------+--------+
| 253406 | Baek      | Olivera    |  38623 |
+--------+-----------+------------+--------+
